Package org.cloudsimplus.traces.vmallocationpolicywithgroups

Class VmAllocationPolicyTraceRecord

java.lang.Object
org.cloudsimplus.traces.vmallocationpolicywithgroups.VmAllocationPolicyTraceRecord
public class VmAllocationPolicyTraceRecord extends Object
A class for creating records of how the VM requests are handled by the VM placement group allocation policies (see VmAllocationPolicyRequestType). The records are used to create trace files.
Since:
CloudSim Plus 7.3.2
Author:
Pavlos Maniotis
See Also:
  • VmAllocationPolicyTraceTableBuilder
